items.desc: Welcome to the Roblox Project: Pokemon Wiki! This wiki is about the game Project: Pokemon on Roblox, created by wish_z (Formerly Wishnite). In this game, you must catch Pokemon who will accompany you and help you defeat other trainers in battle! Explore the Kanto region and defeat all 8 Gym leaders! Once you're strong enough, you can advance ahead and eventually become the Pokemon Champion. Additionally, you can also catch new Pokemon and explore the world. You can trade and battle with other real players too!
